,{"pid":"d82f95be136ccbe84e5639a31b1ac869e6d1e63a","tid":113392,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條腰營養不良</blockquote><br />\n條腰有事都屌打曬所有高達<br />\n如果全盛時期的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一部咁嘅垃圾放多幾枝炮上身就話型<br />\n幾歲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真思考一下<br />\n係心口有支陽電子炮<br />\n但係駕駛倉係心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔熱要幾多層？</blockquote><br />\n放個艙喺枝炮上面咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51f061d63b884576e4dd700227791ca5a4f3723","tid":113392,"uid":46858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條腰營養不良</blockquote><br />\n條腰有事都屌打曬所有高達<br />\n如果全盛時期的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一部咁嘅垃圾放多幾枝炮上身就話型<br />\n幾歲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真思考一下<br />\n係心口有支陽電子炮<br />\n但係駕駛倉係心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔熱要幾多層？</blockquote><br />\n放個艙喺枝炮上面咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n溶腳定溶頭？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabf3c8bee9d91c84e93fa6364da8d6a1e9f453a","tid":113392,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"突自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一開始已經好鐘意自由 <br />\n出埋突自直頭射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6f75e99ef8093ab07a38defe755a67fe1ec818","tid":113392,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條腰營養不良</blockquote><br />\n條腰有事都屌打曬所有高達<br />\n如果全盛時期的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一部咁嘅垃圾放多幾枝炮上身就話型<br />\n幾歲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真思考一下<br />\n係心口有支陽電子炮<br />\n但係駕駛倉係心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔熱要幾多層？</blockquote><br />\n你又知隔熱係一個問題<br />\n唔通你又揸過咩<br />\n就係出色既設計<br />\n所以係艙上面加多支炮 加強火力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17d4ecae4addd235347c4ba435b92c6152f7f3b","tid":113392,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>突自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一開始已經好鐘意自由 <br />\n出埋突自直頭射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當初一出自由，已經覺得機設<br />\n過廿年都唔會覺得柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來仲要出埋突自<br />\n每晚都打十個飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebcfda871fc63c1df0e741e0cc382c2068f2c13","tid":113392,"uid":2538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:26:22.000Z","msg":"個人覺得突擊/自由都型過突擊自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58798257ad9f3ccd272bced4b1aef83dcecd586b","tid":113392,"uid":82332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61429a617b4a2c6fba3a729797ab635d1dd46d23","tid":113392,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5558eb85f8db2793b75240e4a3355d51b70a2dd0","tid":113392,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>突自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一開始已經好鐘意自由 <br />\n出埋突自直頭射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當初一出自由，已經覺得機設<br />\n過廿年都唔會覺得柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來仲要出埋突自<br />\n每晚都打十個飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開始覺得樓主係蝦腸<br />\n自由一出我都覺得柒<br />\n到用五色大炮嗰幕我更加肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8681d7ec476d8938be2d378d97e772eeacafe636","tid":113392,"uid":59501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T17:20:21.000Z","msg":"果陣出機設個個屌個肚臍炮同金色關節<br />\n又笑鳩佢個名柒<br />\n估唔到今日會上神檯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}